title: Code Crunch & Job Hunt: Battle Logs
description: Share your epic (or tragic) tales from the job search battlefield. Did you bravely conquer the coding test, or did it conquer you?

title: Debugging My Resume
description: Need help squashing those pesky resume bugs? Post your CV here and let the community help you refactor it into a job offer magnet.

title: Interview Nightmares & Dream Jobs
description: Spill the beans on your worst interview disasters and celebrate those rare moments when it actually went well. Misery loves company, and so do success stories!

description: Ever wonder if that HR person was a cleverly disguised bot? Share your weirdest and most robotic interactions with hiring departments.

title: Salary Negotiation: The Boss Fight
description: Tips, tricks, and epic fails from the final boss battle of job hunting: salary negotiations. Did you get the loot or just a consolation prize?
